We have agreed on non-back to backs on:<br>
<br>
glyphed cycle (modified - can try it 2x on your day, meaning try,fail,wait,try the instant its up again -- i suppose if you were crazy you could try 3, but that'd be 10ish hours in srae, enough to make one mad!)<br>
